   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Setup</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>App Setup</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Develop</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Custom Settings</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Config System Properties</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Manage</uicontrol>
               </menucascade>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol> next to System Properties.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Enter the Deal Guidance custom page URL in the <uicontrol>Custom Deal Guidance
                  Page</uicontrol> field. For example, enter <i>
                  <xref href="https://na34.visual.force.com/apex/MyCustomDealGuidancePage"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external">
                     <u>https://na34.visual.force.com/apex/MyCustomDealGuidancePage</u>
                  </xref>
               </i> for a custom page named <i>MyCustomDealGuidancePag</i>e.<i/>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <result id="result_o4c_g43_rcc">
         <p>For a selected Quote/Proposal Line Item, you can 'Preview' the custom Deal guidance
            interface and activate the custom page if the preview is satisfactory.</p>
      </result>
